<testgrp id="RM000000W83016X_07_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___000035500000">
<testtitle>CHECK OTHER DTCS OUTPUT (IN ADDITION TO DTC P2714)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect  the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG) and turn the intelligent tester on.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Enter the following items: "DIAGNOSIS / OBD/MOBD / ECT / DTC INFO / CURRENT CODES".</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Read the DTCs using  the intelligent tester.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Display (DTC output)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Only "P2714" is output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>"P2714" and other DTCs</ptxt>
</entry>
